      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Transform your Shopline website search performance with our expert SEO services.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-600 to-red-600 text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
        Get Your Free SEO Audit
      </a>
